query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.score >= 0 AND q1.score <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('electrical-panel',
'insulation',
'np-complete',
'reference-request',
'switch',
'walls',
'water')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('cs',
'diy')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Curious',
'Enthusiast',
'Revival')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
